OL,3,CTranslink to hold talks over the
OL,4,Cweekend to avert three day transport
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FA three day strike by transport
OL,8,Fworkers in Northern Ireland is set to
OL,9,Fgo ahead next week.
OL,11,FUTV understands that Translink is set
OL,12,Fto hold talks over the weekend with
OL,13,Fworkers in an attempt to avert the
OL,14,Faction.
OL,16,FUnless the action is averted,
OL,17,Fthousands of Translink workers on bus
OL,18,Fand rail services are expected to walk
OL,19,Fout for 72 hours from February 27
OL,20,Fafter unions rejected an "inadequate
OL,21,Fpay offer".
