OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FOfficials from the transport unions
OL,8,FGMB, Unite and SIPTU held meetings
OL,9,Fwith Translink on Thursday.
OL,11,FA statement from the unions on Friday
OL,12,Fsaid they "stand ready to enter
OL,13,Ffurther dialogue with the company if
OL,14,Fthey wish to avoid the action by
OL,15,Fimproving on today's offer".
OL,17,FThe statement added: "The 72-hour
OL,18,Fstrike action commencing on a
OL,19,Fstaggered basis from midnight on
OL,20,FFebruary 27 remains in place.
