OL,7,F"Unions are fully prepared to return
OL,8,Fto negotiations provided Translink is
OL,9,Fprepared to make a substantially
OL,10,Fimproved offer."
OL,12,FThe three day strike is the latest in
OL,13,Fa series taken by Translink workers
OL,14,Fover pay and conditions, but will be
OL,15,Fthe longest continual action as part
OL,16,Fof the current dispute.
