OL,7,FLast week, Stormont ministers agreed
OL,8,Fto release #688 million to make
OL,9,Foutstanding pay awards for public
OL,10,Fsector workers in Northern Ireland.
OL,12,FIndividual departments have each been
OL,13,Fgiven an allocation to negotiate with
OL,14,Frelevant trade unions on the pay rises
OL,15,Fthat will be introduced.
OL,17,FHowever, unrest among unions seeking
OL,18,Fpay parity with the rest of the UK has
OL,19,Fcontinued.
